Package: appify
Type: Package
Title: appify: Write R Get Apps!
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Reto", "Wyss", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "reto.wyss.ch@gmail.com")
Description: appify enables you to build apps from function definitions.
    Output from appify can be rendered in an Rmd file or may be saved to
    a file as html. To run apps created with appify you'll need OpenCPU.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
